      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING GRYLLIS (7) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 0.8 lengths at Goulburn in a handy 19.99. Draws out wide but has a good record over this journey. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Hard to fault his recent form and can win again. CLATTERED (4) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing second and beaten 0.8 lengths (20.03) behind ZIPPING GRYLLIS at Goulburn. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. NANGAR ARCHIE (8) has an excellent record here having never missed the placings in four starts, including three wins. Hit the frame latest (18.17) when second at Richmond in a Mix 1/2/3. Looks well placed here and among the chances. NICKO KING (5) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
